#

Pesto Turkey Burger

25 min
$12
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Wheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbHealthy

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

TurkeyBurgerQuick MealHealthy

Description

Juicy turkey burgers infused with fresh pesto, served with a side of sweet potato fries for a delicious and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • pesto sauce: 1/3 cup
  • whole wheat burger buns: 4
  • sweet potatoes: 2 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
